            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1883.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken stock</strong>, <strong>chopped courgette</strong>, <strong>chopped black olives</strong> and <strong>capers</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened slightly </p>",
